OL,3,CVictims of infected blood scandal to
OL,4,Creceive an extra #1 billion from
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FLast month, campaigners described a
OL,13,Flack of progress on the Hillsborough
OL,14,FLaw to prevent future cover-ups as "an
OL,15,Finsult" to victims of major disasters
OL,16,Fand their families.
OL,26,@vD@dOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776243304
OL,3,CVictims of infected blood scandal to
OL,4,Creceive an extra #1 billion from
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FPeople affected by the infected blood
OL,8,Fscandal, the Hillsborough tragedy, and
OL,9,Fthe Horizon Post Office ordeal wrote
OL,10,Fto the prime minister to express their
OL,11,Ffrustration.
OL,13,FThe government has proposed a duty of
OL,14,Fcandour as part of the Public Office
OL,15,F(Accountability) Bill ` also known as
OL,16,Fthe Hillsborough Law ` to meet a
OL,17,Fmanifesto pledge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776243304
OL,3,CVictims of infected blood scandal to
OL,4,Creceive an extra #1 billion from
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FThe proposed legislation takes its
OL,8,Fname from the Hillsborough disaster,
OL,9,Fafter which families campaigned for
OL,10,Fyears to get to the truth behind what
OL,11,Fcaused the crush, which led to the
OL,12,Fdeath of 97 football fans at the FA
OL,13,FCup semi-final between Liverpool and
OL,14,FNottingham Forest in 1989.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776243304
OL,3,CVictims of infected blood scandal to
OL,4,Creceive an extra #1 billion from
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FIt would create a duty for public
OL,8,Fauthorities and public officials to
OL,9,Falways act "with candour, transparency
OL,10,Fand frankness in their dealings with
OL,11,Finquiries and investigations", and to
OL,12,Fflag information to inquiry and
OL,13,Finvestigation leaders, if they think
OL,14,Fit is relevant.
OL,16,FHowever, its progress through
OL,17,FParliament has stalled amid a row over
OL,18,Fwhether people in organisations such
OL,19,Fas MI5 and MI6 would be subject to the
OL,20,Fsame duties as other public servants.
OL,26,@qD@LOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
